OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCharities facing a 'perfect
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstorm' as demand rises     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Hundreds of charities are concerned    
OL,6, about whether they will cope with      
OL,7, rising demand for services this winter,
OL,8, according to research given exclusively
OL,9, to the BBC's Wake Up to Money podcast. 
OL,11,FThe survey of nearly 350 charity       
OL,12,Fmanagers was carried out by the Law    
OL,13,FFamily Commission on Civil Society     
OL,14,Fbetween 18 and 24 October 2021.        
OL,16,FOf those who took part, 210 said they  
OL,17,Fexpected demand to rise this winter.   
OL,19,FThe commission said charities were     
OL,20,Ffacing a "perfect storm" of factors.   
